7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:08+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?\n\n              International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization to meet its more pressing challenges. While it takes time, money and effort to obtain the ISO certificate, it will allow your business to profit from enhanced processes and controls although providing to the organization with additional customer reputation. You will first need to establish and document your manufacturing processes before you can get OHSAS 18001 certified and implementing the right procedures to ensure that you can maintain quality standards."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms focus more on awareness, ISO training and ISO implementation of safety standards to improve industry's best practices and return on investment. Our easy and efficient consulting strategies ensure successful execution at your company. We simplify the process of ISO certification in Dubai and UAE. We appoint a customer representative to direct you and your company through the next steps after we have received your request. Here are the seven essential steps to get ISO 18001 certification in Dubai."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Simple steps to get ISO 18001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 1: Plan"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Create a plan and how to design and prepare documents for the certification process to implementing ISO 18001 in a small or medium-sized company. The process of ISO 18001 certification is an important step which has an impact on the long-term success of OHSAS ISO 18001 certification."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 2: Educate the organization"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"All workers must be qualified in the ISO 18001 health and safety management system."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 3:Design and Document"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Writing the quality plan, procedures and other ISO 18001 documents are considered the most complicated step when implementing OHSAS 18001 standard. Those guidelines should meet the majority of specifications of ISO 18001, which are daunting for many to learn, understand and implement in their organization. The largest segment of the project is to review and update the existing systems to meet most of the requirements. You should check these procedures when you have developed procedures to fulfill the guideline."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18"]}],"$L19"]}]}]
