e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?\n\n              International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?\n\n              International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/important-steps-in-getting-iso-18001-certification-in-ubai"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:08+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"How to get OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai?\n\n              International standards are an essential strategic resource that can help your organization"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1a","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 4: Use and Improve the OHSAS"}]
11:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Once you create and report the system, workers will know the processes, collect documents and enhance the process. The organization will run the OH&S and collect data for about three months or more."}]
12:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 5: Implementation"}]
13:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Now is the time to implement the ISO 18001 health and safety management systems throughout the company. In this step, you will introduce new criteria that you have introduced for affected employees in your 18001 report and will assist them in adapting their working methods accordingly. To make this step to achieve this performance, your employees must know how they benefit from the new processes and specifications. Certainly, these demands that your new processes are useful, non-bureaucratic and easy to understand."}]
14:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 6: Internal Audit"}]
15:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Internal audits of ISO OHSAS 18001 are investigations to verify that all specifications for ISO 18001 are being complied with your organization. These internal audits are directed by the implementation of OHSAS 18001 certification processes but also periodically after achieving ISO OHSAS certification in Dubai. An internal audit is carried out by one or more employees of your company trained in ISO 18001 certification auditing. The internal auditors are responsible for ensuring that your organization meets the requirements of OHSAS 18001 as defined in your latest ISO health and safety strategies and work instructions."}]
16:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 7: Certification"}]
17:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To obtain OHSAS 18001 certification in Dubai, It is necessary to have a free, third-party ISO 18001 certification auditor visit your company and complete the site audit. You can carry out a certification audit immediately after your internal audit has been completed and two months worth of collected records using your ISO OHSAS 18001 processes in UAE."}]
18:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Visit our website and submit queries with all your details to get your business OHSAS 18001 certified in Dubai, UAE. One of our ISO certification experts will contact you as soon as possible to better understand your needs and provide the best solution available on the market."}]
